{
  "stem": "1062.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then after a while, you know, you couldn't breathe because the air was-- you know, you couldn't breathe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was very hard to breathe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It's-- you know-- it's you get terrorized, like, you know, you can't breathe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "A lot of people died that night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I think that was basic training more or less.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The very able bodied to survive something like this was-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The following day we were sitting out-- I'm talking about Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I was in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The following day we were sitting out on the-- on the-- on the sun.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "You know, we were sitting on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The sun beating up-- beating on us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "No food, and no water.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Water was-- we needed water more than food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And a day later, and then I remember one, in the middle of the night-- not the middle, they started that night, where they called everybody who-- was named started with an A to come forward.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And when they went forward, they went ahead and they tattooed a number.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Now my name is Rosenthal, so it's an R.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So I came out there like 1 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And you know-- so one guy just went ahead and he held my hand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And he took a-- a-- a-- like a stick, and he started to-- to punch-- to punch in the number.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my number was A 11832.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A-- A 118-- A 11832.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Forget about it-- I didn't have no more name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was my number.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know what is interesting is that most of the people there that night, they were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those-- and sometimes people, they always think for the better.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They said the reason for the A is because we are Hungarian Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
